19:17.123 --> 19:20.525
-Yeah. I mean, it's very...
           -Come on.

19:20.527 --> 19:22.660
(laughing):
      You are so strange.

19:22.662 --> 19:25.196
-You're so weird.
       -Keep looking up.

19:26.332 --> 19:27.932
-Oh! Ow.
    -(thud, objects clatter)

19:27.934 --> 19:30.034
