     into a pile of rubbish

19:33.106 --> 19:35.139
because I wasn't looking
       where I was going

19:35.141 --> 19:36.374
like a bloody normal person.

19:36.376 --> 19:37.842
Well, you're not
      used to looking up.

19:37.844 --> 19:39.477
