19:39.479 --> 19:42.547
-Seen this?
          -Seen what?

19:42.549 --> 19:44.715
-KATE (laughing): Oh, my God.
          -TOM: Yeah.

19:44.717 --> 19:46.284
I've walked down this street
         so many times.

19:46.286 --> 19:47.785
I've never seen that before.

19:47.787 --> 19:50.054
Like I say. Follow me.

19:51.124 --> 19:52.490
(quietly):
              Ooh.

