54:46.050 --> 54:47.283
Oh, thanks.

54:47.285 --> 54:48.951
<i> -Nabijem i tebe na kurac. </i>
       -MARTA: And you...

54:48.953 --> 54:50.719
y-you sit there, and you think
   it's absolutely acceptable

54:50.721 --> 54:52.121
to say that she's cleverer
