55:28.693 --> 55:31.427
(Ivan speaking Serbo-Croatian)

55:32.496 --> 55:34.430
Marta.

55:34.432 --> 55:36.198
-Marta.
            -Marta.

55:37.668 --> 55:39.268
Eh.

