      trying to find you.

56:57.548 --> 56:59.681
So take your stupid phone
  out of your stupid cupboard

56:59.683 --> 57:01.417
and contact me, all right?
           'Cause...

57:01.419 --> 57:03.552
because I've just been
         really stupid.

57:03.554 --> 57:06.789
I've been
     really, really stupid.

57:06.791 --> 57:08.724
I mean, it's a bit
      of a stretch, but...

57:08.726 --> 57:10.259
have you had a couple drinks?

57:10.261 --> 57:12.628
Oh, bugger off
  with your cleanly manliness.

57:12.630 --> 57:14.763
All right?
 Just... just go back to work.

57:14.765 --> 57:16.198
Leave me alone.

57:16.200 --> 57:18.700
