You're not yourself.

58:53.130 --> 58:54.530
No?

58:54.532 --> 58:55.864
Maybe I'm wrong.

58:55.866 --> 58:57.533
Wrong about what?

58:57.535 --> 59:00.102
Maybe this is more you
         than anything.

59:06.510 --> 59:07.910
I'm a mess.

59:09.046 --> 59:10.579
Kind of.

59:11.582 --> 59:13.615
In here.

59:20.057 --> 59:24.793
When I was ill,
     it was a heart thing.

59:25.996 --> 59:27.930
Right.

59:28.999 --> 59:30.699
