       you'll get weird.

59:36.707 --> 59:38.173
No.

59:40.878 --> 59:42.678
¶ ¶

59:51.388 --> 59:53.288
Is this okay?

01:00:12.376 --> 01:00:15.644
They took out my heart.

01:00:17.147 --> 01:00:20.115
